
Version 0.97
=============

   - Support for time forked calibrations (e.g. LH bias change ->
     FLUXCON change).
   - New S13-compatible calibration set.
   - Improved focus setting and screen redraw in CubeView for a
     variety of tools.
   - Don't lose window focus with multiple CubeViews.
   - Record-level auto bad pixels.
   - Reverse cycle through bad pixel showing states using Shift
     mouse-3.
   - CubeSpec: preserve single wavelength regions.
   - Visualize: handle deleted records correctly.
